4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>출력된 결과!</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token string\">'*******haha!********'</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"center-메소드는\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#center-%EB%A9%94%EC%86%8C%EB%93%9C%EB%8A%94\" aria-label=\"center 메소드는 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>center() 메소드는!</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">첫번째 인자로\n    &#39;변환하고자 하는 문자열의 총 길이&#39;\n\n두번째 인자로\n    &#39;중앙정렬된 문자를 제외한 공간에 채워넣을 문자&#39;\n\n를 받아요!</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"만약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%8C%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"만약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>만약,</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">대상이 되는 문자열이\n\n변환하고자 하는 문자열의 총 길이를 초과하면,\n\n동작하지 않아요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"문자를-항상-일정한-위치에-중앙정렬-시키고-싶다면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90%EB%A5%BC-%ED%95%AD%EC%83%81-%EC%9D%BC%EC%A0%95%ED%95%9C-%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%97%90-%EC%A4%91%EC%95%99%EC%A0%95%EB%A0%AC-%EC%8B%9C%ED%82%A4%EA%B3%A0-%EC%8B%B6%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"문자를 항상 일정한 위치에 중앙정렬 시키고 싶다면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문자를 항상 일정한 위치에 중앙정렬 시키고 싶다면!</h2>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h3 id=\"출처쓰\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B6%9C%EC%B2%98%EC%93%B0\" aria-label=\"출처쓰 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>출처쓰!</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://blockdmask.tistory.com/380\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">’ 개발자 지망생 ’ 님의 티스토리 블로그 !</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/pos